{"tid":152320,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【好刺激咁輸】Bitcoin十分鐘內插逾兩成！因美國拒ETF申請","createTime":"2017-03-11T16:03:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-12T12:21:42.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8c5dd692ff3fbf57826b5e345088e0ba53c000d7","tid":152320,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T16:03:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5fth3g0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5fth3g0.jpg&h=278dd05f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBitcoin昨晚即市圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s634X0k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs634X0k.jpg&h=965b765d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBitcoin日線圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/12/000242_92a72b9ef61d0f8ce47b0502049ee25b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F12%2F000242_92a72b9ef61d0f8ce47b0502049ee25b.jpg&h=60fa5f35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBitcoin近年成為內地走資一大途徑，刺激價格上漲<br />\n<br />\nBitcoin價格昨日chok暈，話說昨日美國證交會（SEC）宣佈拒絕Bitcoin ETF的申請，於是價格由一度急升一成急促下滑，曾經倒跌18%，收市仍跌8.3%，報1,100.56美元。<br />\n<br />\n波幅最大的一段時間，曾經由1280美元以上，十分鐘時間急插至980美元以下，跌幅達25%，波幅足以輸死人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56413413&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170311\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56413413%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170311&d=30ZlKbyCH33W3wkrfz60C26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=c4943a79\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56413413%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170311&h=c32a7d92\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56413413&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170311</a>"},{"pid":"8cbe00939f1d0270c8eb598c16f182bec6